Symbol.Script_3D:
! Design Chair 08.gsm
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then end if not (gs_shadow) then shadow off hotspotoffset = (gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1) * 0.02 ! hotspot áthelyezése simple és detailed mód között if GLOB_CONTEXT>20 and GLOB_CONTEXT<40 then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1
pen gs_cont_pen resol gs_resol
add a/2,b/2,0
!--- Hotspots ------------------------------------------------------------------
unID=1 for i = 1 to 2 hotspot a/2, -b/2, 0, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2, b/2, 0, unID : unID=unID+1
hotspot a/2, b/2, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2, b/2, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2, b/2, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
if gs_full_edit then hotspot a/2-0.075, -b/2 + hotspotoffset, 0, unID, gs_seat_height, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2-0.075, -b/2 + hotspotoffset, -1, unID, gs_seat_height, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2-0.075, -b/2 + hotspotoffset, gs_seat_height, unID, gs_seat_height, 2 : unID=unID+1 endif mulx -1 next i del 2
material gs_frame_mat
!--- Sides ---------------------------------------------------------------------
for i = 1 to 2 addz gs_seat_height + 0.145 prism_ 4, 0.02, -a/2, -b/2, 15, -a/2, b/2 - 0.02, 15, -a/2 + 0.07, b/2 - 0.02, 15, -a/2 + 0.07, -b/2, 15 del 1
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then addx -a/2 + 0.07 roty -90 prism_ 8, 0.02, 0, -b/2, 15, 0, -0.04, 15, 0.06, -0.04, 15, 0.06, 0.02, 15, 0, 0.02, 15, 0, b/2 - 0.02, 15, gs_seat_height + 0.145, b/2 - 0.02, 15, gs_seat_height + 0.145, -b/2, 15
del 2 else prism_ 4, gs_seat_height + 0.145, -a/2 + 0.07, -b/2, 15, -a/2 + 0.07, b/2 - 0.02, 15, -a/2 + 0.05, b/2 - 0.02, 15, -a/2 + 0.05, -b/2, 15 endif
mulx -1 next i del 2
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then prism_ 4, 0.02, -a/2 + 0.05, -0.04, 15, -a/2 + 0.05, 0.02, 15, a/2 - 0.05, 0.02, 15, a/2 - 0.05, -0.04, 15 endif
!--- Seating -------------------------------------------------------------------
addz gs_seat_height - 0.05 prism_ 4, 0.02 + (gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1) * 0.03, -a/2 + 0.07, -b/2 + 0.02, 15, a/2 - 0.07, -b/2 + 0.02, 15, a/2 - 0.07, b/2 - 0.02, 15, -a/2 + 0.07, b/2 - 0.02, 15 del 1
!--- Backrest ------------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then addy b/2 rotx 90 prism_ 8, 0.02, -a/2, gs_seat_height/2, 15, -0.015, gs_seat_height/2, 15, -0.015, gs_seat_height*7/6, 15, 0.015, gs_seat_height*7/6, 15, 0.015, gs_seat_height/2, 15, a/2, gs_seat_height/2, 15, a/2, zzyzx, 15, -a/2, zzyzx, 15 del 2 else addz gs_seat_height/2 prism_ 4, zzyzx - gs_seat_height/2, -a/2, b/2 - 0.02, 15, a/2, b/2 - 0.02, 15, a/2, b/2, 15, -a/2, b/2, 15 endif
!--- Cushion -------------------------------------------------------------------
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then material gs_seat_mat addz gs_seat_height - 0.03 prism_ 4, 0.03, -a/2 + 0.07, -b/2, 15, a/2 - 0.07, -b/2, 15, a/2 - 0.07, b/2 - 0.02, 15, -a/2 + 0.07, b/2 - 0.02, 15 del 1 add -a/2 + 0.075, b/2 - 0.06, zzyzx - 0.1 roty 90 cylind a - 0.15, 0.04 del 2 endif
del 1 end
Symbol.Script_2D:
unID = 1
! ====================================================================== ! SCALE ! ======================================================================
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, returned_parameters det2D
! --- 2D Symbol ----------------------------------------------------------------
if det2D = 1 then call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters ALL gs_SymbolType_m = 3 ! 1:200 if det2D = 2 then call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters ALL gs_SymbolType_m = 4 ! 1:100 if det2D = 4 then call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters ALL ! Symbolic
if (gs_SymbolType_m = 1 or gs_SymbolType_m = 2) and abs(A-B) > eps then hotspot2 0, 0, unID : unID = unID +1 hotspot2 a, 0, unID : unID = unID +1 hotspot2 a, b, unID : unID = unID +1 hotspot2 0, b, unID : unID = unID +1 else unID = unID +4 endif
! --- 1:50 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
if det2D = 3 then PEN gs_cont_pen call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters ALL gs_SymbolType_m=0, MSType = 4 add2 0, b rect2 0, 0, a, -a/30 line2 a/12 + a/30, -a/30, a/12 + a/30, -b line2 a -(a/12 + a/30), -0.02, a -(a/12 + a/30), -b fill gs_fill_type poly2_b 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, a, 0, 1, a, -b, 1, 0, -b, 1, 0, 0, 1 del 1 endif
end
Symbol.Script_VL:
HIDEPARAMETER ALL "A", "B", "zzyzx"
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then if gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` parameters gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D endif
call "2dDetailLevel" parameters gs_detlevel_2D = gs_detlevel_2D, gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, enable2dDetLevels = 2+4+8+16+32
if gs_detlevel_2D_m <> 4 then HIDEPARAMETER "gs_SymbolType" lock "gs_SymbolType", "gs_SymbolType_m" endif
call "fa_ChairSymbol" parameters all stSymbolTypes = stSymbolTypes
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=19
values "gs_resol" range [3, ) values "gs_seat_height" range [a/15+0.03, zzyzx-0.165] values "zzyzx" range [gs_seat_height+0.165, )
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then hideparameter "gs_resol" lock "gs_resol" endif if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then hideparameter "gs_resol", "gs_shadow", "gs_full_edit" lock "gs_resol", "gs_shadow", "gs_full_edit" endif
!--- Minimal Space -------------------------------------------------------------
values "MSFront" range [0,) values "MSSide" range [0,) values "MSRear" range [0,)
Symbol.Script_1D:
eps = 0.001
gs_OrigoCentered = 0
dim stSymbolTypes[16] stSymbolTypes[ 1] = `Круглый` stSymbolTypes[ 2] = `Круглый со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 3] = `Прямоугольный` stSymbolTypes[ 4] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 1` stSymbolTypes[ 5] = `Трапециевидный` stSymbolTypes[ 6] = `Трапециевидный со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 7] = `Криволинейный` stSymbolTypes[ 8] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой` stSymbolTypes[ 9] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[10] = `Прямоугольный со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[11] = `Круглый со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[12] = `Круглый со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[13] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой 2` stSymbolTypes[14] = `Криволинейный со Спинкой 3` stSymbolTypes[15] = `Детальный 1` stSymbolTypes[16] = `Детальный 2`
Symbol.Script_UI:
UI_dialog `Параметры Стула`
ui_current_page gs_ui_current_page
dim tabTitles[4] tabTitles[1] = `Размеры и Минимальное Пространство` tabTitles[2] = `2D-отображение` tabTitles[3] = `3D-отображение и Покрытия` tabTitles[4] = `Характеристики`
dim tabIcons[4] tabIcons[1] = "uiTab_Dimension_flat(1)" tabIcons[2] = "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" tabIcons[3] = "uiTab_3DRepr_flat(1)" tabIcons[4] = "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)"
FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_Dimension_flat(1)" FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_2DRepr_flat(1)" FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_3DRepr_flat(1)" FILE_DEPENDENCE "uiTab_Descriptions_flat(1)"
iPageIDRoot =-1 iPageIDDimMinSpace = 1 iPageID2DRepresentation = 2 iPageID3DRepresentation = 3 iPageIDDescriptions = 4
pageStartY = 5 ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ !UI_PAGES ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
UI_PAGE iPageIDDimMinSpace, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[1], tabIcons[1] gosub "dimMinSpacePage"
UI_PAGE iPageID2DRepresentation, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[2], tabIcons[2] gosub "2DPage"
UI_PAGE iPageID3DRepresentation, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[3], tabIcons[3] gosub "3DPage"
UI_PAGE iPageIDDescriptions, iPageIDRoot, tabTitles[4], tabIcons[4] gosub "descriptionPage"
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ end ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ !Subroutines ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "dimMinSpacePage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
x1 = 0 x2 = 228 y0 = pageStartY + 4
ui_outfield `Высота Сидения`, x1, y0, 168, 15 ui_infield "gs_seat_height", 169, y0 - 4, 90, 19
ui_separator 0, y0 + 21, 444, y0 + 21
pageStartY = pageStartY + 29
call "ui_chairs_minimalspace" parameters MSType = 1, ! MINSPACE_SIMPCHAIR MSSide = MSSide, pageStartY = pageStartY
return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "2DPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ call "ui_object_2DRepresentation" parameters iSymbolClass = 14, gs_SymbolType_m = gs_SymbolType_m, stSymbolTypes = stSymbolTypes, gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m, gs_2DSeat = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type = gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen = gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen = gs_back_pen, iFillListID = iPageID2DRepresentation
return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "3DPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ dim surfacesArray[2] surfacesArray[1] = "gs_frame_mat" surfacesArray[2] = "gs_seat_mat"
dim childFlagArray[2] childFlagArray[1] = 0 childFlagArray[2] = 0
call "ui_object_3DRepresentation" parameters bShowAnimation = 0, surfacesArray = surfacesArray, childFlagArray = childFlagArray, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_resol = gs_resol, gs_shadow = gs_shadow, iSurfaceListID = iPageID3DRepresentation
return
! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ "descriptionPage": ! ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ dim stParamNames[16] stParamNames[1] = "gs_list_cost" stParamNames[2] = "gs_list_manufacturer" stParamNames[3] = "gs_list_note" stParamNames[4] = "gs_list_location" stParamNames[5] = "gs_list_accessories" stParamNames[6] = "FM_Type" stParamNames[7] = "FM_InventoryNumber" stParamNames[8] = "FM_SerialNumber" stParamNames[9] = "FM_ProductionYear" stParamNames[10] = "FM_ObjectWeight" stParamNames[11] = "FM_ObjectWeightUnit" stParamNames[12] = "gs_list_custom1" stParamNames[13] = "gs_list_custom2" stParamNames[14] = "gs_list_custom3" stParamNames[15] = "gs_list_custom4" stParamNames[16] = "gs_list_custom5"
call "ui_object_listing" parameters all listfieldID = iPageIDDescriptions, listFieldPosY = 0, listFieldHeight = 265, stDescHeader = "", stValueHeader = "", stParamNames = stParamNames return
Symbol.Comment: Дизайнерский стул с 2D-символами и минимальным пространством.
